PLAYER STATS HELP
DEXTERITY
Dexterity(DEX): Dexterity is most often used when you are trying to perform some sort of acrobatic feat or another, such as avoiding a fireball or climbing up a wall. It is also used when performing very fine and intricite actions, such as copying a document or aiming a bow. 

See also: ~CREFstats, strength, constitution, speed, willpower, intelligence, empathy, charisma
